{"tid":2134097,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港資智勤控股（9913）IPO招股書指「新冠病毒源於武漢」 遭中資券商抵制禁認購","createTime":"2020-07-31T12:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T08:43:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"907b28652b2e7d44fdfafd2cebaf3d310fd251aa","tid":2134097,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T12:50:06.000Z","msg":"【新增內容】新股本地模板承造商智勤控股（9913）一句「新冠病毒源自武漢」事件發酵，在內地資金「北水」心中舉足輕重的內地港股投資網站「格隆匯」晚上以快訊形式，呼籲投資者抵制認購智勤。格隆匯指，智勤招股書寫到「COVID-19此病毒源自中國武漢」，嚴重違背事實，及污名化武漢，鄭重呼籲所有投資者抵制該股發行，堅決放棄申購。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊（700）為第二大股東的券商富途證券，今晚傍晚突然不再接受智勤的孖展認購，並已刪除由內部撰文有關介紹智勤業務的文章。本報正向富途查詢「跪低」的原因。據了解，中資老虎證券亦已停止認購。<br />\n<br />\n自從中央定調「武漢肺炎」是對中國的污名化，各大上市公司的文件都稱病毒為「COVID-19」或「新冠肺炎」。但昨日開始招股的本地模板承造商智勤控股，在招股書風險因素中清楚寫明「......COVID-19，此病毒源自中國武漢。」英文版為「COVID-19......which was originated from Wuhan」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200731/C7WTVPNZT4GT53WW2OZBLWRO5I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200731%2FC7WTVPNZT4GT53WW2OZBLWRO5I%2F&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOVHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=3a100377\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200731%2FC7WTVPNZT4GT53WW2OZBLWRO5I%2F&h=abed3a83\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200731/C7WTVPNZT4GT53WW2OZBLWRO5I/</a>"},{"pid":"a50e74258377ed3f752597e54aec9fdea1b01da9","tid":2134097,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a09bc9670f922564fa51b6fb0cb8e370ff5d083","tid":2134097,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/03/22/world/coronavirus-spread.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2Fworld%2Fcoronavirus-spread.html&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOVHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=0b5213b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/03/22/world/coronavirus-spread.html</a>"},{"pid":"355dc74b8833f7ae1d66191286e6866b76be9422","tid":2134097,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7phB0pD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7phB0pD.jpg&h=b4ac110a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84fd2325676219c32cab73e8a290cb72b4717bf8","tid":2134097,"uid":173425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"終於有黃色股票圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39162c74e37862b7cf0ea605213be4a3bb2bf7dd","tid":2134097,"uid":104684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:25:04.000Z","msg":"煲大佢，買熊"},{"pid":"095a146961b9f05243c91896d815b440506ec368","tid":2134097,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"有講錯？"},{"pid":"fb373899d8b5e61ece35cb82dc0867906e65aad7","tid":2134097,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:56:59.000Z","msg":"我有興趣"},{"pid":"df446fddbba05a1bc3e22ff75976eaf4551bd4b9","tid":2134097,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f777d32389b20b73759d345d331a65d1c704e951","tid":2134097,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"幾時上市"},{"pid":"868af5c1d7aa29cfb38b23bdcb86528181d6b286","tid":2134097,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:04:06.000Z","msg":"淡友"},{"pid":"738b1b5970aafeb16713e0a5c74fe34f324f91fe","tid":2134097,"uid":103362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:43:14.000Z","msg":"第日招股書講台灣都唔可以"}]}